                            <comment id="142019" author="aromanenko" created="Thu, 11 Feb 2016 20:34:12 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;the lock up happens in function lnet_mt_match_md in case of wrong header of incoming message. The cause of this issue is lnet_mt_match_head() where hash&#8217;s offset is overflowed for unique card&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;wildcard case was fixed in &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-1622&quot; title=&quot;hash MEs on wildcard portal when it&amp;#39;s possible&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-1622&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-1622&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; but uniquecard case wasn&apos;t&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
